gameData

Class Distribution

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameData.Distribution
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExponentialDistribution, NormalDistribution, UniformDistribution

    abstract class Distribution
extends Object
    The Distribution is an abstract class that stores the data of activity's distribution, each Activity has it's own Distribution which is representing activity's effects on player's statistics at depend on time influence (rounds)
    Author:
    Mateusz Szews
